<tr><td><p>&nbsp;</p></td></tr>  <tr>    <td valign='top' align='left' class='news'><p class='boldheader'>THAT'S TWICE NOT THRICE</p><font class='news'>Just in from the test server:
<ul>
The Triple Attack skill has been <b>removed</b> from Rangers. After examining the effects of this skill during actual play, and then further discussion with both the development team and our player base, it became clear that triple attack was not a necessary upgrade to the ranger class. Rangers in their current form do damage appropriate to what we expect, and do not need additional upgrades to damage output. 
<P>
We'll keep you updated on any further adjustment to these melee changes. 
</ul>
You can discuss these changes in our Burning Issues forum.  Click <a href="http://forums.castersrealm.com/cgi-bin/eq/ultimatebb.cgi?ubb=get_topic&f=3&t=002663">here</a> to post.
