Current revisions on test include:
<ul>
<li>Monks and Rangers will get triple attack.</li>
<li>Rangers will get a defensive increase 50+.</li>
<li>Monks will be given a new damage bonus at 55 and again at 60.</li>
<li>Bards will get increased offensive capacity from Level 50+.</li>
<li>Two-Handed weapon damage will be markedly improved.</li>
<li>A retro-active change of ultra high end two handed weapons to improve them is planned.</li>
</ul>
Note these changes are only on test at this time and may not go live.
</font><p class='db'>Click <a href='viewarticle.asp?Article=3780'><b>here</b></a> for details.</p>    <p class='newsig'><font class='newsig'>Submitted by </font><font class='newsiglink'><a href='mailto:baelish@castersrealm.com' class='newsiglink'>Baelish</a></font>, 4:07 AM</p></td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td valign='top' align='left'>&nbsp;</td>  </tr><tr>
