<tr><td><p>&nbsp;</p></td></tr>  <tr>    <td valign='top' align='left' class='news'><p class='boldheader'>SHAMAN EPIC BROKEN?</p><font class='news'>The last patch has broken the Shaman Epic turning it into a heal spell instead of a damage over time one.<P>
The spell is of questionable efect to any Shaman with the Torpor spell as it can currently only be used on the Shaman themself, the enemy, or someone you are duelling (unless you are on a PvP server).<P>
It sounds fairly likely this is a mistake, and should be fixed in the next patch, or by a possible spdat replacement without a server downtime.<P>
<B>Update:</b> We have spoken with Lawrence Poe who has confirmed that this bug has already been fixed in the database, no exact time on when it would be fixed on live servers was available though.
